{
  "stem": "5970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used to pull-- take a bucket of water, throw it on everything, and then just spread it around, and they thought it was all washed.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was the only way I could finish the work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Otherwise I could never have been able to-- to do that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was the routine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The advantages of it were that I had food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- this one woman that was in charge of me gave me food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I must say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and she explained to everybody-- she had to justify her-- her-- her kindness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she used to tell them that I'm not really Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm a mixed-- I'm mixed blood.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I'm not really Jewish, and that's why she's helping me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they asked, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I worked there for all the time while I was in Plaszow, till-- till they took us-- till they sort of started also to liquidate the-- the camp and send everybody away.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they were very happy that I used to-- whatever I could, I used to bring food back with me and share it with everybody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that stage, when I had no family, friendships were formed, and I must say the women helped each other tremendously.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we relied on each other, and the older women looked after the younger ones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- there was a lot of help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- they didn't-- on the contrary, they were-- they were pleased that at least I had food, and I could share some of it with-- with my friends.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, everybody had to have some work, you know, to do something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and this was really something that probably saved my life in the long run.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
